### CheckLargerCands() {#afe58a1278a6b1a8f254a740575a6a102}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>static std::optional&lt; std::pair&lt; IRSimilarityCandidate &#42;, IRSimilarityCandidate &#42; &gt; &gt; CheckLargerCands (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> &amp; CandA, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> &amp; CandB, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap</a>&lt; unsigned, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/denseset">DenseSet</a>&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> &#42; &gt; &gt; &amp; IndexToIncludedCand, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap</a>&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> &#42;, unsigned &gt; &amp; CandToGroup)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Look for larger IRSimilarityCandidates From the previously matched IRSimilarityCandidates that fully contain <code>CandA</code> or <code>CandB</code>.

If there is an overlap, return a pair of structurally similar, larger IRSimilarityCandidates.


<ParametersList title="Parameters">
<ParametersListItem name="[in] CandA">- The first candidate we are trying to determine the structure of.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[in] CandB">- The second candidate we are trying to determine the structure of.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[in] IndexToIncludedCand">- Mapping of index of the an instruction in a circuit to the IRSimilarityCandidates that include this instruction.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[in] CandToOverallGroup">- Mapping of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> to a number representing the structural group assigned to it.</ParametersListItem>
</ParametersList>

### checkNumberingAndReplaceCommutative() {#afbf484050e75f5876a5f490e2047e233}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>static bool checkNumberingAndReplaceCommutative (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap</a>&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> &#42;, unsigned &gt; &amp; SourceValueToNumberMapping, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap</a>&lt; unsigned, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/denseset">DenseSet</a>&lt; unsigned &gt; &gt; &amp; CurrentSrcTgtNumberMapping, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a>&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> &#42; &gt; &amp; SourceOperands, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/denseset">DenseSet</a>&lt; unsigned &gt; &amp; TargetValueNumbers)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Determine if one or more of the assigned global value numbers for the operands in <code>TargetValueNumbers</code> is in the current mapping set for operand numbers in <code>SourceOperands</code>.

The set of possible corresponding global value numbers are replaced with the most recent version of compatible values.


<ParametersList title="Parameters">
<ParametersListItem name="[in] SourceValueToNumberMapping">- The mapping of a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> to global value number for the source IRInstructionCandidate.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[inout] CurrentSrcTgtNumberMapping">- The current mapping of source <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> global value numbers to a set of possible numbers in the target.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[in] SourceOperands">- The operands in the original <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a> in the current instruction.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[in] TargetValueNumbers">- The global value numbers of the operands in the corresponding <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/instruction">Instruction</a> in the other <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/irsimilarity/irsimilaritycandidate">IRSimilarityCandidate</a>.</ParametersListItem>
</ParametersList>

<SectionUser title="Returns">
true if there exists a possible mapping between the source <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/instruction">Instruction</a> operands and the target <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/instruction">Instruction</a> operands, and false if not.
</SectionUser>

</MemberDefinition>
